address2: Beichen Avenue No. 1555 Ouya 1st Road Chanba Ecological District
longBusinessSummary: Sunfonda Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the sale and service of motor vehicles in Mainland China. It sells imported and domestically manufactured luxury and ultra-luxury automobiles. The company also offers after-sales services, such as maintenance and repair services, sale of spare parts, and automobile detailing services; and other value-added services, including automobile insurance agency, automobile financing agency, automobile licensing, and automobile survey services. In addition, it provides logistics and storage services; technology development and internet services; and sale and service of second-hand cars. Further, the company is involved in the recycle and disassemble of motor vehicles; and commercial management business. The company was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Xi'an, the People's Republic of China. Sunfonda Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Top Wheel Limited.
